                <h1>Can You Wallpaper Textured Walls? Tips & Tricks</h1>
                <p>Yes, you can use wallpaper on textured walls, but preparation is key. Smooth the surface as much as possible by filling in deep grooves or holes. Opt for thicker wallpaper or removable options that can adapt better to the texture. Ensure proper adhesion by using a strong wallpaper paste and smoothing out bubbles during application.</p>
